Products.Name: Round Hill Chardonnay 2024 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A bright, golden California Chardonnay with Meyer lemon, pear, and honeysuckle aromas. Creamy butterscotch finish.
Products.Description:
Bright gold color with aromas of Meyer lemon, pear and honeysuckle, with hints of vanilla and cinnamon. Flavors of ripe pear and Meyer lemon with creamy butterscotch on the palate.

Food Pairing: Pairs with popcorn chicken, fish tacos, or light salads.

Products.Name: Round Hill Cabernet Sauvignon 2022 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: An approachable, everyday California Cabernet Sauvignon with blackberry, plum, and caramel notes. Excellent value.
Products.Description:
Deep ruby color with aromas of blackberry, black cherry and caramel. Juicy flavors of plum, blackberry, and caramel. Well-balanced with good acidity, soft tannins and a long, smooth finish.

Food Pairing: Pairs with burgers, pizza, or BBQ ribs.

Products.Name: Round Hill Rosé 2024 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A refreshing, salmon-colored California Rosé with bright strawberry and cassis notes. Perfect for warm-weather sipping.
Products.Description:
Salmon-colored rosé with fresh berry fruitiness. Red berries and strawberries with nuances of cassis on the palate. Discreet acidity and full aromas.

Food Pairing: Pairs with summer salads, grilled shrimp, or fresh fruit.

Products.Name: Round Hill Zinfandel 2022 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A bold, fruit-forward California Old Vine Zinfandel with dark cherry and blackberry character. Excellent value.
Products.Description:
Bold and fruity with ripe berry and spice notes. Aromas of dark cherry, blackberry, and a touch of pepper. Medium to full body with smooth tannins.

Food Pairing: Pairs with grilled sausages, pulled pork, or spicy dishes.

Products.Name: Round Hill Merlot 2022 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A smooth, fruit-driven California Merlot with strawberry, cranberry, and dark chocolate notes. Silky tannins at an accessible price.
Products.Description:
Ruby colored, bright and flavorful with ripe berry, fruit and spice notes. Aromas and flavors of ripe strawberry, cranberry, vanilla and dark chocolate. Soft, elegant mouthfeel with refined, silky tannins.

Food Pairing: Pairs with pasta bolognese, roasted vegetables, or soft cheeses.

Products.Name: Rutherford Ranch Chardonnay 2020 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A round, approachable Napa Valley Chardonnay with baked peach and brioche aromas, finishing with lemon curd and brown butter elegance.
Products.Description:
Notes of baked peach, pie crust and hints of brioche. Bright acid on the palate leads to flavors of lemon curd and citrus cheesecake with hints of fresh sage and brown butter on the finish.

Food Pairing: Pairs well with roasted chicken, creamy pasta, or grilled seafood.

Vivino Rating: 3.7/5 ⭐

Products.Name: Rutherford Ranch Cabernet Sauvignon 2021 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A full-bodied, silky Napa Valley Cabernet with layered aromas of dark fruit and toasty caramel, earning 91 points from both Wine Spectator and James Suckling.
Products.Description:
Opens with aromas of black cherry, black currant, and dark plum layered upon notes of toasty caramel. Full-bodied and silky with flavors of blackberries and Mission figs intermingled by notes of clove and well-integrated tannins. 91 points from both Wine Spectator and James Suckling.

Food Pairing: Pairs beautifully with grilled ribeye, braised short ribs, or aged cheddar.

Vivino Rating: 4.0/5 ⭐

Products.Name: Rutherford Ranch Sauvignon Blanc 2023 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A bright, refreshing Napa Valley Sauvignon Blanc bursting with grapefruit, lime zest, and tropical guava.
Products.Description:
Bright aromas of fresh citrus and tropical flavors with apparent grapefruit, lime zest, and guava.

Food Pairing: Pairs with oysters, goat cheese with honey, or melon and prosciutto.

Vivino Rating: 3.8/5 ⭐

Products.Name: Rutherford Ranch Reserve Cabernet Sauvignon 2019 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A premium Napa Valley Reserve Cabernet with cassis and dark chocolate-covered blueberry flavors, earning 91 points from Decanter.
Products.Description:
Opens with aromas of cassis, black pepper and fresh floral notes. Flavors of dark chocolate-covered blueberries, cherry cola, brandied cherries and raspberry puree. Integrated, silky tannins with a long, round finish. 91 points from Decanter.

Food Pairing: Pairs with filet mignon, lamb chops, or dark chocolate desserts.

Vivino Rating: 4.2/5 ⭐

Products.Name: Rutherford Ranch Reserve Chardonnay 2019 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A rich, layered Reserve Chardonnay from Napa Valley with stone fruit, honey, and crème brûlée character.
Products.Description:
Aromas of baked stone fruit and Manuka honey that lead into a palate of crème brûlée, baked apple streusel, crushed almond brittle, caramel and underlying fresh citrus.

Food Pairing: Pairs with lobster, creamy risotto, or roasted pork loin.

Vivino Rating: 4.1/5 ⭐

Products.Name: Torcia Red Wine 2019 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A handcrafted Napa Valley red blend with savory notes of graphite, dried fig, and candied plums. One of Napa's hidden gems.
Products.Description:
Savory flavors mingle with hints of graphite, dried fig and candied plums. Youthful tannins dance on the palate giving lively, electric texture perfect for drinking now or for aging.

Food Pairing: Pairs with braised lamb, wild mushroom risotto, or aged Gouda.

Vivino Rating: 4.4/5 ⭐

Products.Name: Predator Six Spot Red 2023 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A bold, fruit-forward Lodi red blend of Zinfandel, Petite Sirah, and Malbec with raspberry jam and caramel aromas.
Products.Description:
A vibrant, sweet bouquet of raspberry jam, caramel and cinnamon toast. Excellent oak integration provides silky tannins and spice paired with wild berry fruit. Full of ripe black fruits with notes of clove, black pepper, and sweet tobacco.

Food Pairing: Pairs with BBQ, smoked meats, or spicy Mexican cuisine.

Vivino Rating: 3.9/5 ⭐

Products.Name: Predator Sauvignon Blanc 2022 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A bright, aromatic Sauvignon Blanc with lemon blossom, tropical pineapple, and honeydew notes. Fresh and zesty.
Products.Description:
A bright wine with notes of crushed lemon blossoms, lemon curd, tropical pineapple and ripe honeydew. Fresh, clean palate with bright acidity. Flavors of pineapple, guava, green apple and feijoa.

Food Pairing: Pairs with ceviche, goat cheese salad, or grilled fish.

Products.Name: Predator Chardonnay 2024 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A fruit-driven California Chardonnay with apple, pear, and a creamy touch. The 'Ladybird' label celebrates sustainable vineyard practices.
Products.Description:
Aromas and flavors of roasted fall fruits and nuts, pineapple upside down cake, apple-banana kefir. Medium-to-full body with notes of apple, pear, and citrus with a touch of creaminess. 89 points Tastings.com.

Food Pairing: Pairs with grilled chicken, Thai curry, or creamy appetizers.

Products.Name: Predator Cabernet Sauvignon 2022 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: An intense, full-bodied Lodi Cabernet with dark berries, dark chocolate, and cinnamon spice. Sustainably grown.
Products.Description:
An intense, full-bodied wine with flavors of dark berries and spice. Vibrant aromas of blackberry, cherry and dark chocolate, with subtle notes of cinnamon and toasty oak. 87 points Wine Enthusiast.

Food Pairing: Pairs with grilled steak, hearty stews, or sharp cheddar.

Vivino Rating: 3.8/5 ⭐

Products.Name: Scott Family Estate Pinot Noir 2024 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A soft, decadent Monterey County Pinot Noir from Arroyo Seco with cherry, sage, and raspberry character.
Products.Description:
A soft and decadent 100% Pinot Noir with aromas and flavors of cherry, sage, ripe raspberries, and earthy notes. Richly textured and medium-bodied with balanced acidity and a smooth, lingering finish.

Food Pairing: Pairs with grilled salmon, roasted duck, or mushroom dishes.

Vivino Rating: 3.8/5 ⭐

Products.Name: Four Virtues Zinfandel 2023 (Bottle)
Products.ShortDescription: A robust, bourbon barrel-aged Lodi Zinfandel with raspberry, cherry, and blackberry layered with caramel and vanilla. Bold at 16.8% ABV.
Products.Description:
Deliciously complex and silky smooth Lodi Zinfandel, featuring flavors of bright raspberry, cherry and juicy blackberry, framed by nuanced layers of caramel, vanilla and toasty oak. Aged in French and American oak, finished in charred bourbon barrels. Bold at 16.8% ABV.

Food Pairing: Pairs with smoked brisket, BBQ ribs, or dark chocolate.

Vivino Rating: 4.1/5 ⭐

Products.Name: Rutherford Ranch Cabernet Sauvignon 2019 (3L)
Products.ShortDescription: The acclaimed Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon in an impressive 3-liter format — ideal for events, gifting, or extended cellaring.
Products.Description:
Well-balanced, harmonious and not-too-full-bodied wine with an attractive array of red and black cherries, cedar and bay leaves on a lightly tannic texture. 89 points Wine Enthusiast.

Food Pairing: Perfect for dinner parties — pairs with roasted meats, stews, and hard cheeses.
